### GraphQL - List Orders
POST http://localhost:8081/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ listOrders }"
}

###

### GraphQL - Get Order
POST http://localhost:8081/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ getOrder(id: \"1\") }"
}
